== Installation ==
<!-- add more sections below as necessary, e.g. Wifi, photos, ... -->

Run <code>pmbootstrap init</code> and select beryllium as device.

Choose a display environment of your choice.

Works with mainline: USB, panel (with HW acceleration), keys, WiFi, booting modem, internal storage and SDCard support
(newest kernel not in pmaports yet, have to build it using envkernel)

Works with downstream: USB, panel, touchscreen, keys

